Package: gaschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Georgia School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Georgia Department
    of Education (GaDOE) and Governor's Office of Student Achievement (GOSA).
    Provides functions for fetching enrollment data with demographic and grade-level
    breakdowns and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    httr,
    rappdirs
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    scales
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
